title: Uplift Spice Collection (Japanese Rock)
description:
Tired of lazy English bands that re-hash the same old shit?

Uplift Spice is a Japanese Rock Band that kicks ass.


This collection contains their 5 albums from 2006 to 2009.

Shateki (2006) - 192 kbps
Hanabi no iro (2007) - 128 kbps
Rasen (2007) - 128 kbps
Uplift Spice (2008) - 320 kbps
Omegarhythm (2008) - 320 kbps
